# audit-api-test.http
### Record a new audit log
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/audit/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": "john.doe",
  "action": "VIEW_ACCOUNT",
  "resourceType": "Account",
  "resourceId": "ACC-12345",
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.100",
  "timestamp": "2023-10-27T10:30:00",
  "details": "Viewed account balance"
}

### Get daily stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/audit/reports/daily?date=2023-10-27
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Generate daily report
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/audit/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "reportDate": "2023-10-27"
}

